name: Document Verification for Shortlisted Candidates in List VI and List IV

details.description: The deadline for document verification for shortlisted candidates in List VI and List IV for the states of Haryana, Jammu & Kashmir, Jharkhand, and Maharashtra has been extended up to January 15, 2025.

name: Document Verification for Manipur Division (Special Cycle May-2023 and Schedule-II, July 2023)

details.description: The deadline for document verification for shortlisted candidates in List IV of the Manipur Division has been extended up to January 15, 2025.
